name: Starcounter Under the Hood
tagline: Home Page for Open Source Contributors
body:
### Welcome!

This is the home page for the creators and contributors of the Starcounter DBMS. If you are looking for the Starcounter homepage, please go to [www.starcounter.com](http://www.starcounter.com).

The [GitHub Starcounter project](http://github.com/starcounter/starcounter) contains source code for Starcounter contributors.

The current version of Starcounter is only available under a Commercial License. However, the upcoming version 2.0 will be free for open source projects, personal projects (software owned by a single individual) and non-commercial projects.
